  <chapter is-chapter="true" class="- map/topicref bookmap/chapter " href="#unique_1" type="concept"><topicmeta class="- map/topicmeta " data-topic-id="dbdocsconcept1"><resourceid appid="dbdocsconcept1" class="- topic/resourceid " oxy-source="topic"/><navtitle href="#unique_1" class="- topic/navtitle ">Database Administrator Guide</navtitle><?ditaot gentext?><?ditaot genshortdesc?><shortdesc class="- map/shortdesc ">The NextGen Trading Card Game features exclusive collectible cards inspired by the         Rocket Software NextGen Academy and its Rocketeers. The platform empowers users to buy and         sell new cards and related products, creating a dynamic marketplace for fans and         collectors.</shortdesc><critdates class="- topic/critdates ">
      <created class="- topic/created " date="January 2017"/>
      
    </critdates></topicmeta><topicref class="- map/topicref " href="#unique_2" type="topic"><topicmeta class="- map/topicmeta " data-topic-id="dbdocstopic1"><resourceid appid="dbdocstopic1" class="- topic/resourceid " oxy-source="topic"/><navtitle href="#unique_2" class="- topic/navtitle ">ECOMAPP Database Architecture</navtitle><?ditaot gentext?><?ditaot genshortdesc?><shortdesc class="- map/shortdesc "> Structural and logical architecture for the ECOMAPP NXTCG database on Db2 13 for         z/OS. The database design and architecture includes SKU composition, multiplier-based         pricing, and normalized entities with referential integrity.</shortdesc><critdates class="- topic/critdates ">
      <created class="- topic/created " date="January 2017"/>
      
    </critdates></topicmeta></topicref><topicref class="- map/topicref " href="#unique_3" type="task"><topicmeta class="- map/topicmeta " data-topic-id="installingdb2"><resourceid appid="installingdb2" class="- topic/resourceid " oxy-source="topic"/><navtitle href="#unique_3" class="- topic/navtitle ">Installing ECOMAPP</navtitle><?ditaot gentext?><?ditaot genshortdesc?><shortdesc class="- map/shortdesc ">ECOMAPP database is hosted on Db2 for z/OS platform. Installing ECOMAPP requires you to       have a Db2 license called Db2 Connect in order for you to make a connection from the NXTCG       backend application.</shortdesc><critdates class="- topic/critdates ">
      <created class="- topic/created " date="January 2017"/>
      
    </critdates></topicmeta></topicref><topicref class="- map/topicref " href="#unique_4" type="topic"><topicmeta class="- map/topicmeta " data-topic-id="troubleshootingspectredb"><resourceid appid="troubleshootingspectredb" class="- topic/resourceid " oxy-source="topic"/><navtitle href="#unique_4" class="- topic/navtitle ">Troubleshooting the NXTCG ECOMAPP database</navtitle><?ditaot gentext?><?ditaot genshortdesc?><shortdesc class="- map/shortdesc ">There are common SQL and API error codes when configuring the ECOMAPP database. Solutions         are provided for each issue.  </shortdesc><critdates class="- topic/critdates ">
      <created class="- topic/created " date="January 2017"/>
      
    </critdates></topicmeta></topicref></chapter>
  
  
